    dc:description "FIGURE 42. a) Andricus sp. (Ref.: MEX: P141); b) Andricus sp. (Ref.: MEX: P230); c) Melikaiella bicolor (Ref.: MEX: 044, 049, P026, P071); d) Sphaeroteras sp. (Ref.: MEX: P024); e) Undetermined genus (Ref.: MEX: P184); f) Neuroterus sp. (Ref.: MEX: P386, P388); g) Disholcaspis sp. (Ref: MEX: P398); h) Femuros nr repandae (Ref.: P187, P227, 2797); i) Femuros repandae (Ref.: MEX: P313, 255, 256); j) Andricus sp. (Ref.: MEX: P314); k) Disholcaspis sp. (Ref.: MEX: P140); l) Undetermined genus (Ref.: MEX: P259); m) Neuroterus sp. (Ref.: MEX: P381); n) Loxaulus hyalinus (Ref.: MEX: 333); o) Undetermined genus (Ref.: Clark-49); p) Atrusca sp. (Ref.: P317, P318); q) Atrusca sp. (Ref.: MEX: P183); r) Andricus sp. (Ref.: MEX: P394); s) Andricus sp. (Ref.: MEX: P038)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4434112/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4434040>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Synergus diversicolor Lobato-Vila & Pujade-Villar, sp. nov. Female: a) head in frontal view; b) head in dorsal view; c) antenna; e) propodeum; f) tarsal claw; g) radial cell of the fore wing; h) mesosoma in lateral view (dark morphotype); i) mesosoma in lateral view (light morphotype); j) mesosoma in dorsal view (dark morphotype); k) mesosoma in dorsal view (light morphotype); l) metasoma in lateral view; m) detail of the syntergum punctuation. Male: d) detail of the first antennal segments." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4434040/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4434038>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Synergus diversicolor Lobato-Vila & Pujade-Villar, sp. nov. Dark morphotype: a) female lateral habitus; b) male lateral habitus. Light morphotype: c) female lateral habitus; d) male lateral habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4434038/files/figure.png" ;
